4.2. Results
Some categories, such as ‚Äútomato‚Äù, ‚Äúpear‚Äù and ‚Äúapple‚Äù can successfully be categorized with a short query, constisting of 3 to 10 clauses. Adding more clauses would not have had any noteworthy eÔ¨Äect on the results, e.g. only
adding a single image. The most complex queries were generated for the animals ‚Äúcow‚Äù, ‚Äúhorse‚Äù and ‚Äúdog‚Äù.
